<bibRefCitation author="Virkki, N. &amp; J. A. Santiago-Blay" box="[583,962,738,762]" pageId="19" pageNumber="18" pagination="79 - 99" refId="ref28398" refString="Virkki, N., and J. A. Santiago-Blay. 1994. Chromosomes of some neotropical flea beetles (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Alticinae) with inherently univalent, amphiorientating sex chromosomes and meioformula 11 + X + y in the male meiosis. Cytobios 80: 79 - 99." type="journal article" year="1994">Virkki and Santiago-Blay 1994</bibRefCitation>
